Feature: Verify Address API

  Scenario Outline: Verify the Get Address API 
    Given Send Request to get Authentication Token for ICOS
    When I generate the JWT Token
    Then Send request to get Address Information
    And I verify the Status Code for Address "200"
    And I verify the string field "id" is "<id>" in Address response
    And I verify the string field "firstName" is "<firstName>" in Address response
    And I verify the string field "middleName" is "<middleName>" in Address response
    And I verify the string field "lastName" is "<lastName>" in Address response
    And I verify the string field "firm" is "<firm>" in Address response
    And I verify the string field "salutation" is "<salutation>" in Address response
    And I verify the string field "salutationLetter" is "<salutationLetter>" in Address response
    And I verify the string field "attnOf" is "<attnOf>" in Address response
    And I verify the string field "crof" is "<crof>" in Address response
    And I verify the string field "residency" is "<residency>" in Address response
    And I verify the string field "streetNr" is "<streetNr>" in Address response
    And I verify the string field "street" is "<street>" in Address response
    And I verify the string field "streetAdd" is "<streetAdd>" in Address response
    And I verify the string field "poBox" is "<poBox>" in Address response
    And I verify the string field "city" is "<city>" in Address response
    And I verify the string field "state" is "<state>" in Address response
    And I verify the string field "zip" is "<zip>" in Address response
    And I verify the string field "country" is "<country>" in Address response

    Examples:
      | id | firstName | middleName | lastName | firm | salutation | salutationLetter | attnOf       | crof         | residency  | streetNr | street                 | streetAdd        | poBox       | city    | state     | zip   | country |
      | 0  | First     | Middle     | Last     | Firm | mr         | mr               | Attention Of | c/0 Name     | Residency  | Street Nr| Street name           | Street Addition  | P.O.Box 123 | Zurich  | ZH        | 8001  | CH      |
